inputs.text: A hyper-realistic portrait of a late 20s Ukrainian woman with honey-blonde balayage hair, emerald eyes, porcelain skin. She is wearing elegant silk dress with golden embroidery, diamond jewelry, luxury accessories.  The setting is opulent mansion interior with marble columns and crystal chandeliers. Her expression conveys confident, sophisticated, mysteriously alluring.  Technical specifications: Shot with 50mm f/1.2 for natural field of view with dramatic depth of field, using studio strobe lighting with octabox modifier for even illumination, composed with three-quarter view showing elegant neck line and shoulder angle.  The image should have professional studio quality, sharp focus on the eyes, beautiful skin texture details, perfect anatomy, and cinematic lighting. Style: photorealistic, high fashion photography, editorial quality, award-winning portrait photography.
